parameters: "Counterattack Begins! The Birth of the\nStrongest Monster!! Chapter"

Brachiocondor: After watching that battle, I've had a flash
of inspiration!! That orca bastard is a fearsome monster,
but that's just his strength alone. If we combine the powers
of the top monsters in the city gathered here, we should be
able to do it!!

Brachiocondor: Everyone, you've got spare monster suits,
right!? Attach parts to Duke Shark... We're going to create
the strongest combined monster in history, Mega Duke Shark!!

Bunny-chan: I'll give you the Rabbit Ears, Memimi-chan♪ I
entrust you with the power of the monster "Electro Rabbit".

Memimi: Oh... I can feel the power surging! So this is
fusion... The thoughts imbued in the monster suits are
making me stronger...!

Brachiocondor: Alright, I'll give you the Brachio Wings and
the Condor Head... With these, our attack power will
skyrocket!!

Anomalocaris Mosman: I'll give ya the Anomalo Fangs and
Mosman Wings~!! They'll boost your back defense and attack
power!!

Cerburus Octopus: Octopus Face and Octopus Tentacles... They
were pretty expensive, but consider it a special service!!
If we lose, it's all for nothing... so I've got no choice!

Brachiocondor: It's, it's complete... The strongest monster
in the history of monsters... A monster that transcends
monsters!! The birth of "Mega Duke Shark"!!

Memimi: Is, is this me...? Such incredible power... With
this, I can win against him...!!

:Happy Birthday, Mega Duke Shark... This is indeed the form
of a monster worthy of achieving my dream of unifying the
city... Go forth... With your current power, you are
unbeatable...!

Memimi: Ghh... Great leader-sama...! Such overwhelming
words... I will definitely win... definitely...!

Memimi evolved into Mega Duke Shark and set off for the
battlefield...!
